summary:
- **Cancellation of Previous Announcement**: Convertible note facility is closed and will no longer be issued (originally announced 27/3/2025).  
- **Proposed Placement**:  
  - **Security Type**: Existing class (CC9 Ordinary Shares).  
  - **Number of Shares**: 18,500,000 issued under 15% placement capacity (no shareholder approval required).  
  - **Pricing**: VWAP-based, at investor’s discretion from 1/6/2025; unpaid shares may be sold/transferred at maturity.  
  - **Purpose**: To fulfill obligations under the convertible note facility (no dividend policy change).  
- **Additional Placement**: 1,500,000 shares pending shareholder approval (refer to 27/3/2025 announcement).  
- **Key Date**: Estimated issue date 2/6/2025.
